<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
  <title>Brave UX - Work - DCV</title>
  <%- include ../partials/_head %>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrapper case-study dcv">
    <header class="case-header">
      <div class="case-header-content container">
        <h5 class="case-header-client-name">Discovery Communications Ventures</h5>
        <h1 class="case-header-tagline">Introducing a&nbsp;<br />start-up adventure</h1>
        <h6 class="case-header-type">Venture Initiative Launch Website</h6>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="case-exec-summary padded blue">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="case-exec-summary-text">We designed and built the debut of a website showing venture activity worthy of the Discovery Communications legacy.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-breakdown padded dark-blue">
      <div class="container row between">
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Challenge</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            Earning venture street cred
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            Discovery wanted the venture capital world to know that one of the most popular cable networks in television history is committed to investing in the future.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Solution</p>
          <h3 class="case-breakdown-summary">
            A gripping vision of the future
          </h3>
          <p class="case-breakdown-detail">
            An online launch that captures Discovery’s unique strengths to a global audience of innovators and entrepreneurs.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="case-breakdown-box column gutter">
          <p class="case-breakdown-heading">Scope</p>
          <ul class="case-breakdown-list">
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Information Architecture</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Visual Design</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">Front-end Development</li>
            <li class="case-breakdown-list-item">HTML5 Anmiation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top overflow light-blue">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-right padded-bottom">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">A debut worth a&nbsp;watch</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Discovery Communications Ventures is an investment initiative of Discovery Communications, the world's #1 pay-TV programmer. Discovery reaches nearly three billion cumulative subscribers in more than 220 countries and territories and is dedicated to satisfying curiosity and entertaining viewers with high-quality content through its global brands.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl dcv-home">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-bottom shadow sr-right lazy-ratio" data-width="1442" data-height="1016">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/desktop-home.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile light absolute sr-bottom sr-delay">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/mobile-home.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/sharks.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column half-md hide-overflow">
        <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="136" data-height="150">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/icons-media.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-left">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/icons-enterprise.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-left">
          <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/icons-blue-skies.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image absolute sr-stagger-left">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md dark-blue">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">A venture fund apart</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            We identified what makes this venture initiative unique through a bespoke visual language of scenes, ideas, and icons.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top light-blue overflow">
      <div class="inner-block padded-bottom row absolute-center-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content content-centered container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">A tale for screens large and small</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Discovery Communications’ content is available in your living room or in your pocket, and the the DCV website follows suit with fully responsive design and code.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block row dcv-displays">
        <div class="container-narrow">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-bottom shadow sr-tall lazy-ratio" data-width="1564" data-height="1646">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/desktop-portfolio.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-mobile light shadow absolute sr-left sr-delay">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/mobile-portfolio.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="frame frame-tablet-vertical light shadow absolute sr-right sr-delay">
            <div class="frame-container">
              <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/tablet-portfolio.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image inherit">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block blue">
      <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/earth-storm.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row">
      <div class="inner-block column half-md hide-overflow">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="955" data-height="929">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/introduction.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image sr-left">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md dark-blue">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">A personal introduction</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Although the DCV launched without a team section, we created the ability to enable this feature in the future
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block extra-padded blue">
      <div class="row container">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="lazy-ratio" data-width="300" data-height="87">
            <img data-normal="./images/work/dcv/education-graphic.svg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain sr-left">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md gutter-bottom-mobile order-top-xs column half-md one-third-lg half-xl">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">A plan for growth</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              A built-from-scratch WordPress back-end allows DCV to change and evolve alongside the teams and individuals it invests in.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column absolute-center-xs half-md dark-blue">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="case-referral-blockquote">Brave UX ensures we achieve this mission.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block padded column half-md light-blue">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text">We are committed to the future of the industry and propelling promising companies forward. Brave UX ensures we achieve this mission.</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Brinton Miller, <em>SVP, Technology Strategy & Architecture</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <%- include ../partials/_footer-scripts %>

</body>
</html>
